{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-projects-post-template-js","path":"/projects/20210305 - Corona Simulator/basic/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<hr>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/eee58ae5964cbdc098a4cc48da6939a5/d43b4/initial.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Sim Initialize\"\n        title=\"Sim Initialize\"\n        src=\"/static/eee58ae5964cbdc098a4cc48da6939a5/fcda8/initial.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/eee58ae5964cbdc098a4cc48da6939a5/12f09/initial.png 148w,\n/static/eee58ae5964cbdc098a4cc48da6939a5/e4a3f/initial.png 295w,\n/static/eee58ae5964cbdc098a4cc48da6939a5/fcda8/initial.png 590w,\n/static/eee58ae5964cbdc098a4cc48da6939a5/efc66/initial.png 885w,\n/static/eee58ae5964cbdc098a4cc48da6939a5/c83ae/initial.png 1180w,\n/static/eee58ae5964cbdc098a4cc48da6939a5/d43b4/initial.png 1202w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Inspired by <a href=\"https://youtu.be/gxAaO2rsdIs\" target=\"_blank\">this</a> beautiful video by <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYO_jab_esuFRV4b17AJtAw\" target=\"_blank\">3Blue1Brown</a>, I tried making a simulation of the spread of Covid-19.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://souruly.github.io/P5-Playground/Corona_Spread_Simulation/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">Link to Sim</a></p>\n<p>Please open this link in a new tab and read along.</p>\n<p>Each circle represents a person moving randomly through space, and each collision counts as a contact. As people come into contact with each other, the disease spreads through the population.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/091431fd50137df7e97e37c685cf0052/690c6/started.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Sim Start\"\n        title=\"Sim Start\"\n        src=\"/static/091431fd50137df7e97e37c685cf0052/fcda8/started.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/091431fd50137df7e97e37c685cf0052/12f09/started.png 148w,\n/static/091431fd50137df7e97e37c685cf0052/e4a3f/started.png 295w,\n/static/091431fd50137df7e97e37c685cf0052/fcda8/started.png 590w,\n/static/091431fd50137df7e97e37c685cf0052/efc66/started.png 885w,\n/static/091431fd50137df7e97e37c685cf0052/c83ae/started.png 1180w,\n/static/091431fd50137df7e97e37c685cf0052/690c6/started.png 1201w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\nNow as you can see, some people are getting infected(<font color=\"#ff007f\">red</font>) while most are still safe(<font color=\"#85db25\">green</font>).</p>\n<p>We assume that the vaccine is going to be invented at some point of time. After which, people start getting vaccinated(circles randomly turn blue).</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c75445140637067f774940c88682f285/d326d/middle.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Sim Start\"\n        title=\"Sim Start\"\n        src=\"/static/c75445140637067f774940c88682f285/fcda8/middle.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c75445140637067f774940c88682f285/12f09/middle.png 148w,\n/static/c75445140637067f774940c88682f285/e4a3f/middle.png 295w,\n/static/c75445140637067f774940c88682f285/fcda8/middle.png 590w,\n/static/c75445140637067f774940c88682f285/efc66/middle.png 885w,\n/static/c75445140637067f774940c88682f285/c83ae/middle.png 1180w,\n/static/c75445140637067f774940c88682f285/d326d/middle.png 1197w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\nOnce all paramenters are set, we start the simulation and take a look how the virus spreads, how many people get vaccinated(<font color=\"#3399ff\">blue</font>), how many people would never even come in contact with the virus(still <font color=\"#85db25\">green</font>) and how many people would unfortunately die(hollow circle).</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Simulating the spread of Covid-19","author":"Sourav Kulkarni","date":"17 March, 2020"},"excerpt":"Inspired by this beautiful video by 3Blue1Brown, I tried making a simulation of the spread of Covid-19. Link to Sim Please open this link inâ€¦","timeToRead":1}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/projects/20210305 - Corona Simulator/basic/","templatePath":"./src/templates/projects-post-template.js"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}